{"word":"G5348 - φθάνω - phthánō - fthan'-o - Attain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φθάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phthánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fthan'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Attain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வா, அடை, முந்திக்கொள், தேறியிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to come before, precede, anticipate"},{"paragraph":"2. to come to, arrive at"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently a primary verb; to <i>be beforehand</i>, that is, <i>anticipate</i> or <i>precede</i>; by extension to <i>have arrived</i> at: - (already) attain, come, prevent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4399/4399\">G4399</a>, <a href=\"#/G5348/5348\">G5348</a>"}]}